35
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:36,840
Eat.

36
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:38,879
Come on, eat.

37
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:43,759
Mhm.

38
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:44,960
Tasty.

39
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:46,879
It's been over twenty years.

40
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:48,319
It hasn't been easy.

41
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:49,919
Back then, the shopkeeper

42
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:52,039
just had a little pushcart,

43
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:52,840
selling them

44
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,000
on the street.

45
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,439
At that time,

46
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,800
I was hot-headed.

47
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,000
I offended the gang boss back then.

48
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:01,300
(Wonton)

49
00:03:01,599 --> 00:03:02,400
Stop right there!

50
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,960
- Stop!
- Stop!

51
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,140
(Young Du Shisan)

52
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,039
Stop!

53
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:06,919
Stop!

54
00:03:09,159 --> 00:03:09,560
Stop!

55
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,319
You again? One bowl, right?

56
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:12,520
Extra wontons, yeah?

57
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:15,719
Quick, hide!

58
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:26,400
Guess

59
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,439
