60
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,319
What?

61
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,199
What's it got to do with me?

62
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,319
I haven't even introduced myself.

63
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:35,280
Me,

64
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:37,360
I just hang around the streets.

65
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,759
Friends call me Du Shisan.

66
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,300
In Fengxi City, north and south,

67
00:03:40,310 --> 00:03:42,170
in South City's nine streets
and twelve alleys,

68
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,280
all kinds of shops,

69
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:44,719
over three hundred.

70
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:47,439
I roughly manage
one hundred and eighty-two of them.

71
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,159
Everything I just mentioned,

72
00:03:49,159 --> 00:03:50,680
all the shops, they're here.

73
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,919
Come be the young master of Qian Gang.

74
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:54,879
What do you say?

75
00:03:55,639 --> 00:03:56,479
(Could it be)

76
00:03:57,039 --> 00:03:58,080
(him?)

77
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,199
We don't even know each other.

78
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,879
And you want to hand me
such a big operation?

79
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,919
Is it because

80
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:08,280
I've got some special talent?

81
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,280
Of course you do.

82
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:14,039
My men told me
you survived a deadly situation

83
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,759
and even dodged a bullet.

84
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,560
So that's why, huh.

85
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,680
This is my goddaughter,

86
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,759
Little Qi Tuotuo.

87
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:28,360
She's

88
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,839
very mischievous.

89
00:04:30,110 --> 00:04:32,390
I offered her the position
of the Seventh Hall's master,

90
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:32,879
she refused.

91
00:04:33,330 --> 00:04:34,839
Insisted on roaming the world instead.

92
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:37,120
Didn't expect her to run into you.

93
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,839
You two really are fated.

94
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:46,000
Hey.

95
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:47,480
That's not fate.

96
00:04:47,759 --> 00:04:49,160
I'm marrying her to you.

97
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:50,730
What do you say?

98
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:51,839
Don't worry.

99
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:55,000
She'll definitely be the good wife,
loving mother type.

100
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,279
Qi!

101
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:57,920
