104
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,279
Qi!

105
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,279
Stop!

106
00:05:05,279 --> 00:05:06,580
This is the one I told you about,

107
00:05:06,639 --> 00:05:07,759
