110
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:20,399
Hey!

111
00:05:20,410 --> 00:05:21,360
I didn't agree to this!

112
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,399
Gently.

113
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:24,879
Gently.

114
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:27,000
Don't come near me!

115
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:27,879
Stop!

116
00:05:27,879 --> 00:05:28,360
Don't move!

117
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:30,240
You're my husband,
of course I have to take a good look.

118
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:30,879
Stay back!

119
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:34,480
Stay back!

120
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,279
Aiya...

121
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,639
Over twenty years

122
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,519
