125
00:06:19,940 --> 00:06:24,900
(Dong Mianhua Wonton)

126
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,480
Hey!

127
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,199
Ow!

128
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:40,639
Qi.

129
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,160
You must work hard to be a good wife.

130
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:44,560
Mhm.

131
